flowRoot.flowPara: start turning red after they reach perhaps 70-80% as they approach peak temp/min fuel.

The colour of the tacho fill (blue) is blue for until the area around 5.5k revs and transitions from blue to bright red completely by 7.5k revs. The fill doesn't all change colour, as the speed increases it reveals more of the bar (and the upper part is red), unlike the fuel and temp.
Pressable buttons/indicators (left right indicators, headlight (off/low/high), break, ABS active etc)
Old analogue counters that rotate around.
